## Install/Upgrade
[ttkDesigner](https://github.com/ceccopierangiolieugenio/pyTermTk/tree/main/apps/ttkDesigner)
 is available on [PyPI](https://pypi.org/project/ttkDesigner/)
```bash
pip3 install --upgrade ttkDesigner
```
## Run
```bash
ttkDesigner
```
